# Atomic Design Rules

UI components follow the **Atomic Design pattern**.

Atoms

Button
Input
Icon
Label
Text

Atoms must:

- be reusable
- contain no business logic
- contain only UI behavior

---

Molecules

Small UI combinations.

Example

SearchInput
FormField

---

Organisms

Large UI blocks.

Example

Navbar
Header
ProductCard

---

Templates

Layout structures.

Example

DashboardLayout
ProductLayout

---

Pages

Pages contain real data and compose templates or widgets.

---

# Important Rule

Atomic UI components must never contain feature logic.
